title: Command Medium Wire Toggle Hooks, Damage Free Hanging Wall Hooks with Adhesive Strips, No Tools Wall Hooks for Hanging Organizational Items in Living Spaces, 7 White Hooks and 8 Command Strips
description: Command White Medium Wire Hooks let you decorate and organize how you want, when you want, without damaging surfaces. A great home improvement item, these no damage wall hooks stick on a variety of smooth surfaces without leaving holes, marks or sticky residue. Use these hanging hooks to hang hats, calendars, keys, measuring spools, cleaning tools, jewelry and other small items. Simply mount these indoor wall adhesive hooks on painted walls, finished wood, painted concrete cinder blocks, laminate, glass, metal and tiles and enjoy the damage free hanging of your favorite small decorations and organizers. Perfect for home renovators and college students, use these wall hooks for hanging decorations and organizers in your home, office, apartment or dorm room to elevate the appearance of your living or working space without tools. Directions are included; follow the directions closely to use the wall hangers as intended. A clever decorating and organizing solution that doesn’t damage surfaces, these Medium Wire tool free wall hangers will help you fearlessly change your space. One package contains 7 white wire toggle hooks and 8 medium adhesive strips. Each single wall hanger can hold up to 2 pounds. Decorate, organize and celebrate damage free with Command.
